  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Persons with COPD are randomized to pedometer versus pedometer plus Internet mediated website
      to promote walking and physical activity. Primary outcome is daily step counts. Intervention
      lasts 3 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
